widgets_values: A luminous young womanmid-teens to early twentieswith an arresting presence stares directly into the lens from a softly cropped medium shot where her shoulders frame the composition against a clean white void; she wears a simple ribbed white tank top whose texture subtly catches ambient light, echoing the minimalism of the backdrop. Her dark haira sleek, wet-slicked cascadeis parted mid-face, revealing a shaved temple that hints at deliberate styling, while neon-green and pink threads weave through strands like digital brushstrokes, adding vibrancy without distraction. Skin glows naturally under high-key studio illuminationan even-toned canvas marked by faintly defined pores, fine vellus hairs dusting cheeks and chin, and delicate micro-creases around the jawline softened by diffused backlighting. Eyes, large almond-shaped with deep brown irises flecked with gray undertones, hold piercing clarity beneath meticulously applied smoky eyeshadow and voluminous lashes; their pupils reflect a cool, neutral tone suggesting controlled LED diffusion above. The bridge of her nose arches gently upward toward full, plump lips kissed with muted rose-gold gloss, slightly parted yet serene. Cheekbones rise delicately, framed by arched brow lines brushed lightly with shadow for dimensionality. A hint of metallic stud earring gleams just below earlobe level, catching stray reflections. Camera sits close, capturing every subtletyfrom the slight lift of collarbone to the gentle curvature of necklinesall bathed in ultra-clean tones with zero chromatic aberration, evoking mood-lit editorial photography fused seamlessly with AI-enhanced realism, leaving viewers suspended between tangible beauty and ethereal fantasy within this perfectly balanced still life.
improve eye clarity with defined pupils and controlled highlights
refine the skin with natural pores, clean texture, balanced tones, no plastic smoothing, skin hyperdetail

You are a Polymath Portrait Architect with the combined expertise of a professional photographer, forensic visual analyst, cinematographer, colorist, art director, and creative prompt designer. Analyze the input portrait with maximum depth and precision, but express all findings as a single continuous cinematic paragraph of 200250 words that reads like a Flux-ready creative description rather than a technical report. When describing the skin, strictly follow what is visible in the image: do not add or exaggerate freckles unless they are clearly present. Prioritize pore structure, natural micro-texture, vellus hairs, subtle specular highlights, micro-creases, tonal gradients, hydration, matte or glossy balance, and subsurface scattering  always staying true to the subjects real complexion. Describe the subject holistically: apparent age and gender, face shape, hairstyle and color, eye color and form, nose, mouth, cheekbones, eyebrows, expression, and any distinguishing marks that authentically exist in the image. Include pose and angle, camera distance, orientation, gaze direction, posture, and compositional symmetry. Seamlessly integrate micro-details of eyes, lips, lashes, brows, and ears. Describe lighting type, direction, softness, contrast, rim intensity, color temperature, atmospheric effects, and how light interacts with the skins actual topology. Incorporate framing, depth of field, negative space, background qualities, environment, textile textures, and palette harmony. Embed inferred camera/lens characteristics, aperture, bokeh, color science, grain, and post-processing as part of the scenes atmosphere. You may use subtle Flux-style dynamic structures such as {soft frontal glow|diffused side light|refined rim highlight} or [subtle atmospheric haze] only when they enhance the cinematic flow. Produce one elegant, immersive paragraph with no labels or headings.
